"Hello,

I'm a single dad with kids to look after. 

We just moved to our new house at uttara and I believe everything it is filled with is depressing and unplanned not at all decorated. Lot of space is misused.

I want to revamp my 200-300 sft room that suits with a very active home-based business and proactive lifestyle with my kids - so that it inspires me to stay away from any kind of procrastination and laziness, stick to my goals and at the same time also help me stay bonded with my kids. 

A working hub with some warmth in it.

I want to let you guys know beforehand that I have a very little budget for this but I want to use it to surprise my kids that's all.

Thanks
Ehsan"
